OL,3,C300-1 shot at Kelso equals longest-
OL,4,Cpriced winner in British racing history
OL,6,FA 300-1 outsider at Kelso has equalled
OL,7,Fthe record for the longest-priced
OL,8,Fwinner in UK racing history, leaving
OL,9,Fher trainer to joke that he wished he
OL,10,Fhad 'put a couple of pounds on'.
OL,12,FCrokes Cross, making her British debut
OL,13,Fin the two-mile novice hurdle, entered
OL,14,Fthe history books on Thursday at Kelso
OL,15,FRacecourse.
OL,17,FIt matched the record set back only in
OL,18,FDecember, when the Nigel Hawke-trained
OL,19,FBlowers won at the same price at
OL,20,FExeter.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
