CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1775408751
OL,3,C300-1 shot at Kelso equals longest-
OL,4,Cpriced winner in British racing history
OL,6,FThe win earned trainer Stuart Coltherd
OL,7,Fhis first success since March 2025, in
OL,8,Fspectacular fashion.
OL,10,F"I never had a penny on. I wish I
OL,11,Fhad!" Coltherd told Racing TV shortly
OL,12,Fafterwards.
OL,14,F"I couldn't say what's been going
OL,15,Fwrong (at the yard up until now). We
OL,16,Fjust had horses maybe too high in the
OL,17,Fhandicap. We had lots placed, they
OL,18,Fjust weren't getting their head in
OL,19,Ffront.
OL,26,@wD@GpmwD@`pn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
