OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1775408751
OL,3,C300-1 shot at Kelso equals longest-
OL,4,Cpriced winner in British racing history
OL,6,F"If I knew it was going to change
OL,7,Ftoday, I might have had a couple of
OL,8,Fpounds on! It's good for everybody to
OL,9,Fget another winner.
OL,11,F"When I saw she was 300-1, I did think
OL,12,Fthat was a huge price, and she works
OL,13,Fwell at home ` it's too late now."
OL,15,FKelso had been the stage for the
OL,16,Fprevious record, with 250-1 shot
OL,17,FPreviously Equinoctial having won at
OL,18,Fthe track back in 1990.
